text: Just saw a LinkedIn Influencer with 'Organic Growth' written in the profile headline.

Jobseekers, this one’s for you.
Every application, every interview, every rejection — it’s all a step closer.
Looking for jobs on LinkedIn is like online dating: Full of promises, mostly ghosting.
LinkedIn scams be like: 'Congratulations, you've been selected for a role you never applied for!'

sapne dekhna achi baat hai,
lekin job ka sapna dekh ke 'interested' dabana aur kuch nahi karta.
